349
00:22:11,911 --> 00:22:14,053
The first type of scattering

350
00:22:14,053 --> 00:22:17,413
is the Mie scattering.

351
00:22:17,413 --> 00:22:22,240
It takes place when 
the radius of the grains

352
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:25,187
is much larger than
the photon's wavelength.

353
00:22:25,187 --> 00:22:29,208
In this case the extinction coefficient
is equal to the one given by the Mie scattering

354
00:22:30,560 --> 00:22:33,579
