355
00:22:33,778 --> 00:22:37,464
Another property is that this
type of scattering is directional,

356
00:22:37,464 --> 00:22:40,488
it is not isotropic – 
it means that 

357
00:22:40,488 --> 00:22:42,372
photon do not scatter

358
00:22:42,372 --> 00:22:43,762
in a random direction.

359
00:22:43,762 --> 00:22:46,137
They rather scatter in a direction

360
00:22:46,137 --> 00:22:52,002
that lies closer to 
the incidence direction.

361
00:22:52,002 --> 00:22:53,718
This is the Mie scattering.

362
00:22:53,718 --> 00:22:58,316
Another type of scattering
is the Rayleigh scattering

363
00:22:58,316 --> 00:23:01,109
that takes place when the medium
consists of small particles -

364
00:23:01,109 --> 00:23:04,245
