369
00:23:19,221 --> 00:23:22,347
In conclusion, if light 
is scattered by large grains

370
00:23:22,347 --> 00:23:25,447
the scattering is directional

371
00:23:25,467 --> 00:23:29,505
and is more effective
for shorter wavelengths.

372
00:23:29,752 --> 00:23:32,042
The dependence law is λ^-1.

373
00:23:32,042 --> 00:23:35,714
The Rayleigh scattering arises
